olice (ASP) Olaniyan Mojeed. “The victims who were occupants of a grey Toyota Sienna were hurriedly rescued and conveyed in the official ambulance attached to the Senate President to the Mother and Child hospital, Ubulu Okiti, along three Benin – Asaba expressway for urgent medical attention.” Vanguard By Henry Umoru President of the Senate, Senator Ahmad Lawan, Sunday, commiserated with the victims of the recent fire outbreak in a major market in Maiduguri, Borno state. Several shops and property worth millions of naira were reportedly destroyed in the incident at Kasuwar Jagol, a major GSM phone market… November 3, 2019 In "News" ABUJA - PRESIDENT of the Senate, Senator Ahmad Lawan on Thursday reiterated that the Senate will only deal with the board members of the  Delta Development Commission, NDDC  it screened and confirmed this month. November 28, 2019 In "News" Stakeholders of the All Progressives Congress (APC) in Ndokwa nation of Delta have lent their support to the party’s choice of Sen. Ahmad Lawan  (Yobe-North East) for the top job of the President of the Senate. March 29, 2019 In "News"